xt-Pirates-film.html|archive-date=21 June 2010|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nIn December 2009, Pattinson autographed a guitar to be auctioned off for charity.<ref name=\"guitar charity\">{{cite web|url=http://www.gossipcop.com/perez-strikes-bad-chord-with-Robert-pattinson-guitar-story|date=18 March 2010|title=Perez strikes bad chord with Robert Pattinson guitar story|work=[[Gossip Cop]]|publisher=Gossip Cop|accessdate=18 March 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100323003809/http://www.gossipcop.com/perez-strikes-bad-chord-with-robert-pattinson-guitar-story/|archive-date=23 March 2010|url-status=live}}</ref> He also volunteered for the ''[[Hope for Haiti Now: A Global Benefit for Earthquake Relief]]'' in January 2010.<ref name=\"mtv-liveblog\">{{cite web|url=http://newsroom.mtv.com/2010/01/22/hope-for-haiti-live-blog|archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20100309012017/http://newsroom.mtv.com/2010/01/22/hope-for-haiti-live-blog/|url-status=dead|archive-date=9 March 2010|date=22 January 2010|title=Hope For Haiti Now: A Global Benefit For Earthquake Relief|first=Kyle|last=Anderson|website=[[MTV News]]|accessdate=23 January 2010}}</ref> ''[[GQ]]'' and ''Glamour'' both named him the \"Best Dressed Man\" of 2010, with ''GQ'' stating, \"Extremely elegant and inspiring, the true essence of a contemporary man.\"<ref>{{cite web|work=[[Glamour (magazine)|Glamour UK]]|url=http://www.glamourmagazine.co.uk/celebrity/celebrity-news/2010/01/05/robert-pattinson-named-gqs-best-dressed-man|title=Robert Pattinson named GQ's Best-Dressed Man|date=February 2013|access-date=26 February 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510160556/http://www.glamourmagazine.co.uk/celebrity/celebrity-news/2010/01/05/robert-pattinson-named-gqs-best-dressed-man|archive-date=10 May 2013|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson And Cheryl Cole Are Named The Best Dressed of 2010|url=http://www.entertainmentwise.com/news/52763/Robert-Pattinson-And-Cheryl-Cole-